{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tipping-content-js","path":"/mongolia","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>In Mongolia tipping is rarely ever expected except in tourism-related services like tour guides. Waiters, taxis, and hotel attendants do not expect tips. Sometimes taxis will attempt to overcharge you by refusing to give change back, but this has nothing to do with gratuity. Some nicer restaurants and hotels in the capital do often add fees to the bill for service, especially for larger groups.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/mongolia","title":"Mongolia","author":"Joni","date":"2019-11-22","image":"mongolia.jpg"}},"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5,"src":"/static/372eacf2f9eab6057c62e9ab8c93d1a9/90537/mongolia.jpg","srcSet":"/static/372eacf2f9eab6057c62e9ab8c93d1a9/b3ebb/mongolia.jpg 270w,\n/static/372eacf2f9eab6057c62e9ab8c93d1a9/95b54/mongolia.jpg 540w,\n/static/372eacf2f9eab6057c62e9ab8c93d1a9/90537/mongolia.jpg 1080w,\n/static/372eacf2f9eab6057c62e9ab8c93d1a9/3cda3/mongolia.jpg 1620w,\n/static/372eacf2f9eab6057c62e9ab8c93d1a9/1f682/mongolia.jpg 2160w,\n/static/372eacf2f9eab6057c62e9ab8c93d1a9/cf1cd/mongolia.jpg 3504w","sizes":"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"image":"mongolia.jpg"}}}